{"lemma":"بَلاغٌ","slug":"بَلاغٌ","root":"ب.ل.غ","root_slug":"ب-ل-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَلاغ","root":"بلغ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":15},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3236","n3237","n3241"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%BA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"notification, communiqué, statement, notice, memorandum","examples":[{"text":"بَلَاغ كَاذِب","english":"a false call"},{"text":"مَتَى مَا يَسُؤْ ظَنُّ ٱمْرِئٍ بِصَدِيقِهِ / يُصَدِّقْ بَلَاغَاتٍ يَجِئْهُ يَقِينُهَا"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of بَلَغَ (balaḡa)."},"ipa":["/ba.laːɣ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3236","headword_ar":"بَلَاغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboliygN","text_ar":"تَبْلِيغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibolaAgN","text_ar":"اـِبْلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bringing, conveyance, delivery,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"communication,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.,) of a message [&c.]. (Jel in iii. 19, &c.) [It often occurs in the Kur as meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"communication,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"announcement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of what is revealed.] ―         -b2-  In a trad., in which it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~u raAfiEapK rafaEato A_ilayonaA mina AlbalaAgi","text_ar":"كُلُّ رَافِعَةٍ رَفَعَتْ اـِلَيْنَا مِنَ البَلَاغِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufiEato ElynA","text_ar":"رُفِعَتْ علينا"},{"kind":"text","text":",] it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is communicated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"announced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA balaga","text_ar":"مَا بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Kur-án and of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"statutes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordinances,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sunan","text_ar":"سُنَن"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino *awiY AlbalaAgi","text_ar":"مِنْ ذَوِى البَلَاغِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aboliygi","text_ar":"التَّبْلِيغِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those who have the office of communicating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"announcing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the simple subst. being put in the place of the inf. n.: (K, TA:) but some relate it differently, saying ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Albul~aAgi","text_ar":"مِنَ البُلَّاغِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the communicators,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"announcers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hud~aAv","text_ar":"حُدَّاث"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHad~ivuwn","text_ar":"مُحَدِّثُون"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and some say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlbilaAgi","text_ar":"مِنَ البِلَاغِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlmubaAligiyna fiY Alt~aboliygi","text_ar":"مِنَ المُبَالِغِينَ فِى التَّبْلِيغِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those who do their utmost in communicating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"announcing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Hr, K.) [See this trad. cited and explained more fully in the first paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rfE","text_ar":"رفع"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA balaAgN liln~aAsi","text_ar":"هٰذَا بَلَاغٌ لِلنَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xiv. last verse], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This"},{"kind":"text","text":"Kur-án contains"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sufficient exposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demonstration, for men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bulogapN","text_ar":"بُلْغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n3237","headword_ar":"بِلَاغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3241","headword_ar":"بُلَّاغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}